name: params_apply

Constants: MAX_ROW_TILES=3, MAX_COL_TILES=2. Shared memory accessors:
shV, shC, SHV(t,i,j), SHA(i,j), ST(i,j). Global memory: GLVT, GLF,

block_apply_3/2/1, block_apply_3_by_1/2_by_1/1_by_1 variants.
